---
title: Five-Spice Chicken Soup with Udon Noodles and Bok Choy
description: Nothing warms us up like a hearty bowl of soup! Udon noodles is a thick wheat flour noodle from Japan, and we love it's chewy texture! We're sure you will enjoy this as much as we do!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/five-spice-chicken-soup-b4e1e959.jpg
